name: Descent Into The Dark
Lore: 'Jedi training is a journey into the depths of an apprentice''s subconscious, where one must learn to use the Force wisely. ''A Jedi''s strength flows from the Force.''',
Text: 'During your turn, if either player just placed a card in a Used Pile, deploy on table. All Used Piles are immediately re-circulated. When any player places one or more cards in a Used Pile, Immediate Effect canceled.',
